House Beautiful has been published since 1896 and is currently published by the Hearst Corporation, which began publishing it in 1934. Smithsonian magazine, on the other hand, was first published in 1970 by the Smithsonian Institution. Given that House Beautiful has a longer history and has been published by at least two different groups (the original publisher and Hearst Corporation), while Smithsonian has been consistently published by the Smithsonian Institution since its inception, it can be concluded that House Beautiful has been published by a greater number of groups.